{
  "stem": "6016.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And yes, I remember too that when it was, I think, Purim, [NON-ENGLISH], the offering, used to go with a little plate to put on a cube of chocolate on a piece of cake, and an apple if we could afford.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I remember very well the cube of chocolate.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Not a block of chocolate, how you call it, but a cube, a small piece of chocolate.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE] That was candies.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "No, candies I don't remember, but I remember very vividly the chocolate.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] I really don't remember exactly.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Being still in a young age, I wanted-- I didn't know the existence-- oh, yes, I, I remember I went visiting to my aunt, so I saw another town, which opened my eyes a little.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But there was no time to dream.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "No, no, I was too young, too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the last-- just before the war, I think, there was the family, we got the little business, where to iron the clothes.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They call it a [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was like a heavy box and a wax inside.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It used to be operated by hand.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And later on, it was operated by a motor, so the electric one was much easier.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I to put, like roll up the, the [BACKGROUND NOISE] clothes, sheets, and shirts, and towels, and make it like a roll, and to roll it under this, which operated the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it came out with a shine, just like ironing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You didn't have to iron.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I was only one who operated it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was physical work.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And sometime my sister helped me too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My mother occasionally too, yes, but she was practically the housewife.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE] And my father was busy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The brothers did not help, no.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
